-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê FUNCTIONS ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

local function updatePlayerList()
    for _, child in ipairs(playerListFrame:GetChildren()) do
        if child:IsA("TextButton") then
            child:Destroy()
        end
    end
    
    local playerList = Players:GetPlayers()
    local yOffset = 0
    
    for _, plr in ipairs(playerList) do
        if plr ~= player then
            local playerBtn = Instance.new("TextButton")
            playerBtn.Size = UDim2.new(1, -8, 0, scale.DROPDOWN_HEIGHT - 4)
            playerBtn.Position = UDim2.new(0, 4, 0, yOffset)
            playerBtn.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(45, 45, 50)
            playerBtn.Text = ""
            playerBtn.AutoButtonColor = false
            playerBtn.BorderSizePixel = 0
            playerBtn.ZIndex = 251
            playerBtn.Parent = playerListFrame
            
            local playerBtnCorner = Instance.new("UICorner")
            playerBtnCorner.CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 6)
            playerBtnCorner.Parent = playerBtn
            
            local playerBtnLabel = Instance.new("TextLabel")
            playerBtnLabel.Size = UDim2.new(1, -10, 1, 0)
            playerBtnLabel.Position = UDim2.new(0, 5, 0, 0)
            playerBtnLabel.BackgroundTransparency = 1
            playerBtnLabel.Text = plr.DisplayName .. " (@" .. plr.Name .. ")"
            playerBtnLabel.TextSize = scale.TEXT_SIZE - 1
            playerBtnLabel.Font = Enum.Font.Gotham
            playerBtnLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_PRIMARY
            playerBtnLabel.TextXAlignment = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left
            playerBtnLabel.TextTruncate = Enum.TextTruncate.AtEnd
            playerBtnLabel.ZIndex = 252
            playerBtnLabel.Parent = playerBtn
            
            playerBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
                selectedPlayer = plr
                playerDropdownLabel.Text = plr.DisplayName .. " (@" .. plr.Name .. ")"
                playerDropdownLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_PRIMARY
                playerListFrame.Visible = false
            end)
            
            playerBtn.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
                playerBtn.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY
            end)
            
            playerBtn.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
                playerBtn.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(45, 45, 50)
            end)
            
            yOffset = yOffset + scale.DROPDOWN_HEIGHT
        end
    end
    
    playerListFrame.CanvasSize = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, yOffset)
end

local function switchTab(tab)
    currentTab = tab
    
    if tab == "BUG" then
        bugTab.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.TAB_ACTIVE
        bugTabLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_PRIMARY
        playerTab.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.TAB_INACTIVE
        playerTabLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
        
        bugContent.Visible = true
        playerContent.Visible = false
    else
        bugTab.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.TAB_INACTIVE
        bugTabLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
        playerTab.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.TAB_ACTIVE
        playerTabLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_PRIMARY
        
        bugContent.Visible = false
        playerContent.Visible = true
        updatePlayerList()
    end
end

bugTextBox:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Text"):Connect(function()
    local length = string.len(bugTextBox.Text)
    bugCharCounter.Text = tostring(length) .. " / 750"
    
    if length > 750 then
        bugTextBox.Text = string.sub(bugTextBox.Text, 1, 750)
    end
    
    if length >= 10 then
        bugCharCounter.TextColor3 = COLORS.SUCCESS
        bugMinCharsLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.SUCCESS
    else
        bugCharCounter.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
        bugMinCharsLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
    end
end)

playerTextBox:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Text"):Connect(function()
    local length = string.len(playerTextBox.Text)
    playerCharCounter.Text = tostring(length) .. " / 500"
    
    if length > 500 then
        playerTextBox.Text = string.sub(playerTextBox.Text, 1, 500)
    end
    
    if length >= 5 then
        playerCharCounter.TextColor3 = COLORS.SUCCESS
        playerMinCharsLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.SUCCESS
    else
        playerCharCounter.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
        playerMinCharsLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
    end
end)

local function showPanel()
    mainFrame.Visible = true
    mainFrame:TweenPosition(
        UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 0, scale.PANEL_TOP),
        Enum.EasingDirection.Out,
        Enum.EasingStyle.Quad,
        0.4,
        true
    )
end

local function hidePanel()
    mainFrame:TweenPosition(
        UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 0, -500),
        Enum.EasingDirection.In,
        Enum.EasingStyle.Quad,
        0.3,
        true,
        function()
            mainFrame.Visible = false
            bugTextBox.Text = ""
            playerTextBox.Text = ""
            bugStatusLabel.Text = ""
            playerStatusLabel.Text = ""
            bugSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY
            playerSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY
            selectedPlayer = nil
            playerDropdownLabel.Text = "Click to select player..."
            playerDropdownLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
            playerListFrame.Visible = false
        end
    )
end

-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê EVENTS ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

openButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    showPanel()
end)

closeButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    hidePanel()
end)

bugTab.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    switchTab("BUG")
end)

playerTab.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    switchTab("PLAYER")
end)

playerDropdown.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    playerListFrame.Visible = not playerListFrame.Visible
    if playerListFrame.Visible then
        updatePlayerList()
    end
end)

bugSubmitButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    local reportText = bugTextBox.Text
    
    if reportText == "" or string.len(reportText) < 10 then
        bugStatusLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.SECONDARY
        bugStatusLabel.Text = "‚ö† Min 10 chars!"
        
        local originalPos = bugTextBoxCard.Position
        for i = 1, 3 do
            bugTextBoxCard.Position = originalPos + UDim2.new(0, 4, 0, 0)
            wait(0.04)
            bugTextBoxCard.Position = originalPos + UDim2.new(0, -4, 0, 0)
            wait(0.04)
        end
        bugTextBoxCard.Position = originalPos
        return
    end
    
    bugSubmitButton.Active = false
    bugSubmitText.Text = "‚è≥ SENDING"
    bugSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
    
    sendBugReport:FireServer(reportText)
    
    wait(0.5)
    bugStatusLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.SUCCESS
    bugStatusLabel.Text = "‚úì Sent!"
    bugSubmitText.Text = "‚úì SENT"
    bugSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.SUCCESS
    
    wait(1.5)
    hidePanel()
    bugSubmitButton.Active = true
    bugSubmitText.Text = "üì§ SUBMIT"
end)

playerSubmitButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    local reason = playerTextBox.Text
    
    if not selectedPlayer then
        playerStatusLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.SECONDARY
        playerStatusLabel.Text = "‚ö† Select player!"
        
        local originalColor = playerDropdownStroke.Color
        for i = 1, 3 do
            playerDropdownStroke.Color = COLORS.SECONDARY
            wait(0.1)
            playerDropdownStroke.Color = originalColor
            wait(0.1)
        end
        return
    end
    
    if reason == "" or string.len(reason) < 5 then
        playerStatusLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.SECONDARY
        playerStatusLabel.Text = "‚ö† Min 5 chars!"
        
        local originalPos = playerTextBoxCard.Position
        for i = 1, 3 do
            playerTextBoxCard.Position = originalPos + UDim2.new(0, 4, 0, 0)
            wait(0.04)
            playerTextBoxCard.Position = originalPos + UDim2.new(0, -4, 0, 0)
            wait(0.04)
        end
        playerTextBoxCard.Position = originalPos
        return
    end
    
    playerSubmitButton.Active = false
    playerSubmitText.Text = "‚è≥ SENDING"
    playerSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_MUTED
    
    sendPlayerReport:FireServer(selectedPlayer.UserId, selectedPlayer.Name, reason)
    
    wait(0.5)
    playerStatusLabel.TextColor3 = COLORS.SUCCESS
    playerStatusLabel.Text = "‚úì Report sent!"
    playerSubmitText.Text = "‚úì SENT"
    playerSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.SUCCESS
    
    wait(1.5)
    hidePanel()
    playerSubmitButton.Active = true
    playerSubmitText.Text = "üì§ REPORT PLAYER"
end)

openButton.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
    TweenService:Create(openButton, TweenInfo.new(0.2), {
        BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY_HOVER
    }):Play()
end)

openButton.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
    TweenService:Create(openButton, TweenInfo.new(0.2), {
        BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY
    }):Play()
end)

closeButton.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
    closeButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.SECONDARY
    closeIcon.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_PRIMARY
end)

closeButton.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
    closeButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.CARD
    closeIcon.TextColor3 = COLORS.TEXT_SECONDARY
end)

bugSubmitButton.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
    if bugSubmitButton.Active then
        bugSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY_HOVER
    end
end)

bugSubmitButton.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
    if bugSubmitButton.Active then
        bugSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY
    end
end)

playerSubmitButton.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
    if playerSubmitButton.Active then
        playerSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY_HOVER
    end
end)

playerSubmitButton.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
    if playerSubmitButton.Active then
        playerSubmitButton.BackgroundColor3 = COLORS.PRIMARY
    end
end)

